title: Celebrity big brother s14e01 pdtv.x264.mp4
description:
Here we go again, who will enter?

The fly-on-the-wall fun begins once more as Emma Willis invites a
fresh group of famous faces to move in together and have their every
word and move recorded for the enjoyment of the viewing public. The
house has been given a glamorous makeover, but the celebrities would
be foolish to expect their usual VIP treatment and should be
prepared for countless twists, turns and tough tasks guaranteed to
cause drama and tension from day one
